short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Prevents you from accidentally visiting index.hu

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Index.hu used to be the primary news source for many of us, and we still routinely and often without thinking type index.hu into our browser's address bar. This extension will redirect you to telex.hu, where the former journalists of index.hu continue to work free of external influence.
